<div id="review_543063729" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/543063729" />
    <a title="Amal M." class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/12334357-amal-m"><img alt="Amal M." src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1346512122p2/12334357.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/543063729?book_show_action=true">Feb 21, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Amal M." class="user" itemprop="url" name="Amal M." href="/user/show/12334357-amal-m">Amal M.</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer543063729" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer326044908308122887">It is rare to read a writer&apos;s own view about the world as he sees it and still be inspired. Through my reading I thought this man must have lived and gained his experience through his life and delivered to us the essence of his experience, but it was a shock to know that his just as young as many of us. But still, his age did not stop him from putting into words what most of us feel and think. Whether the writer wrote about his own (relatively short) experience, or he poured other experiences in</span>
  <span id="freeText326044908308122887" style="display:none">It is rare to read a writer's own view about the world as he sees it and still be inspired. Through my reading I thought this man must have lived and gained his experience through his life and delivered to us the essence of his experience, but it was a shock to know that his just as young as many of us. But still, his age did not stop him from putting into words what most of us feel and think. Whether the writer wrote about his own (relatively short) experience, or he poured other experiences in the same bowl with his own, I still respect the words written in this book.</span>
  <a data-text-id="326044908308122887" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


